<taxonomicName id="4C14838FFFE11745FCFDC6BBFBDB90AF" authorityName="Penard" authorityYear="1910" box="[889,1127,450,476]" class="Lobosa" family="Difflugiidae" genus="Difflugia" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Arcellinida" pageId="3" pageNumber="102" phylum="Amoebozoa" rank="species" species="subaequalis">
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FCFDC6BBFBDB90AF" box="[889,1127,450,476]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">Difflugia subaequalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by more rounded shell, smaller aperture, different shell covering; from 
<taxonomicName id="4C14838FFFE11745FCF0C69AFBBF908F" authorityName="Penard" authorityYear="1902" box="[884,1027,482,508]" class="Lobosa" family="Difflugiidae" genus="Difflugia" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Arcellinida" pageId="3" pageNumber="102" phylum="Amoebozoa" rank="species" species="lithoplites">
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FCF0C69AFBBF908F" box="[884,1027,482,508]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">D. lithoplites</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by shape and size of aperture and different shell covering; from 
<taxonomicName id="4C14838FFFE11745FD4BC57AFC22936F" authorityName="Gauthier-Lievre et Thomas" authorityYear="1958" box="[719,926,514,540]" class="Lobosa" family="Difflugiidae" genus="Difflugia" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Arcellinida" pageId="3" pageNumber="102" phylum="Amoebozoa" rank="subSpecies" species="lebes" subSpecies="sphaerica">
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FD4BC57AFC22936F" box="[719,926,514,540]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">D. lebes sphaerica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C14838FFFE11745FC59C57AFB16936F" authorityName="Schonborn" authorityYear="1965" box="[989,1194,514,540]" class="Lobosa" family="Difflugiidae" genus="Difflugia" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Arcellinida" pageId="3" pageNumber="102" phylum="Amoebozoa" rank="subSpecies" species="lebes" subSpecies="masurica">
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FC59C57AFB16936F" box="[989,1194,514,540]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">D. lebes masurica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by more rounded shell, aperture size and shell covering; from 
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FCE4C55AFB9C934F" box="[864,1056,546,572]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">
<taxonomicName id="4C14838FFFE11745FCE4C55AFC41934F" authorityName="Ogden" authorityYear="1991" box="[864,1021,546,572]" class="Lobosa" family="Difflugiidae" genus="Difflugia" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Arcellinida" pageId="3" pageNumber="102" phylum="Amoebozoa" rank="species" species="geosphaira">D. geosphaira</taxonomicName>
by
</emphasis>
more rounded shell, absence of collar, by aperture shape and size; from 
<taxonomicName id="4C14838FFFE11745FCB0C53AFC7C932F" authorityName="Dujardin" authorityYear="1837" box="[820,960,578,604]" class="Lobosa" family="Difflugiidae" genus="Difflugia" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Arcellinida" pageId="3" pageNumber="102" phylum="Amoebozoa" rank="species" species="globulosa">
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FCB0C53AFC7C932F" box="[820,960,578,604]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">D. globulosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by more rounded shell, smaller size of the aperture; different shell covering; from 
<taxonomicName id="4C14838FFFE11745FCE6C51AFC4A930F" authorityName="GauthierDujardin, Wallich, Lievre" authorityYear="1864" box="[866,1014,610,636]" class="Lobosa" family="Difflugiidae" genus="Difflugia" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Arcellinida" pageId="3" pageNumber="102" phylum="Amoebozoa" rank="species" species="globularis">
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FCE6C51AFC4A930F" box="[866,1014,610,636]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">D. globularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by more rounded shell, much smaller size of the aperture, different shell covering; from 
<taxonomicName id="4C14838FFFE11745FC4AC5FAFB6C93EF" authorityName="Gauthier-Lievre et Thomas" authorityYear="1958" box="[974,1232,642,669]" class="Lobosa" family="Difflugiidae" genus="Difflugia" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Arcellinida" pageId="3" pageNumber="102" phylum="Amoebozoa" rank="variety" species="minuta" variety="grandis">
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FC4AC5FAFBF893EF" box="[974,1092,643,668]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">D. minuta</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FBF8C5FBFB6C93EF" box="[1148,1232,642,668]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">grandis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by more rounded shell form and different shell covering. Diagnostic characters of 
<emphasis id="B960241EFFE11745FBE8C5DBFB6D93CF" box="[1132,1233,674,700]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="102">Difflugia</emphasis>
species are given in table 2 and on fig. 8–28.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
